snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade - Season VII: Wolves of Ragnarok (Release Trailer)
snippet.description: Ragnarok is here. Will you meet a warrior’s end and find your destiny in the Valkyries’ embrace, or will you send your foes hurtling to the ashen depths of Helheim? Embark on an epic new saga in Season VII: Wolves of Ragnarok, now available as a free update in Conqueror’s Blade:  https://conqblade.com/news/756
